        Build a table showing information about the columns in a specific table.
        Parameters:
        columnNames - The names of the columns in this table.
        types - The types of the columns in this table.
        dataTypes - All the possible types a column can have.
        allowBlanks - Booleans indicating whether or not a column allows blank values.
        defaultValues - The default value for each column.
        ids - The ids for each column.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - Thrown when there is a difference in the length of the different arrays. Not applicable to the dataTypes array as entries don't correspond to specific columns.
